graph TB
    subgraph Frontend
        UI[Streamlit UI]
        Client[API Client]
    end

    subgraph Backend
        API[FastAPI Backend]
    end

    subgraph DataStorage
        DB[(SQLite Database)]
    end

    subgraph ExternalServices
        FMP[Financial Modeling Prep API]
        EODHD[EOD Historical Data]
    end

    subgraph MonorepoRoot
        Config[config/ accounts and symbols]
        Examples[examples/ sample data]
    end

    UI <-->|Account and Security Data| Client
    Client <-->|HTTP Requests| API
    API <-->|Read/Write| DB
    API <-->|Fetch Market Data| FMP
    API <-->|Fetch Market Data| EODHD
    UI -->|CONFIG_DIR| Config
    API -->|Optional| Examples
